Just to be sure we have adequate coverage, you should also add valid `break`/`continue` cases in a `static {}`:

```ts
class C {
  static {
    outer: break outer; // valid
    loop: while (v) {
      if (v === 1) break loop; // valid
      if (v === 2) continue loop; // valid
      if (v === 3) break; // valid
      if (v === 4) continue; // valid
    }
    switch (v) {
      default: break; // valid
    }
  }
}
```

